  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Frame agreement with NGO (SASK)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s goal is to help create an independent and democratic trade union movement in the Indian call-centre field. In practice, this means supporting the call-centre employees&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99; trade union founded in 2005, UNITES Professionals India. Because the call-centre business is very new in India and because the existing unions have not represented its employees, UNITES has to develop its own operating model from scratch. Recruitment happens mainly through New Generation Networks (NGN), where recruitment methods and styles that attract youths are used.</narrative>
  </description>
